    com.codename1.ui.animations.Animation, com.codename1.ui.Editable, com.codename1.ui.events.StyleListener, java.lang.Iterable<com.codename1.ui.Component>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AddDefaultPromptPage, ChangePromptComponents, GraphSelectionPage, MultiPromptsPage, NotificationPage, PromptListPage
    class DefaultPageComponents
extends com.codename1.ui.Form
    Parent class that holds/controls the default components used by every Page. Creates a top inset and back button. Confirm/Next button must be created by calling the appropriate functions Functions to call for no Confirm button: initDefault(), createDefaults() For Confirm button as well: initDefault(), initConfirmButton(), createDefaults()
